Jaw Lock.desc: Prevents user and opponent from switching out.

Surging Strikes.desc: Always results in a critical hit and ignores stat changes.

Swallow.desc: The more times the user has performed Stockpile, the more HP is recovered.

Venoshock.desc: Inflicts double damage if the target is poisoned.

Wring Out.desc: The higher the opponent's HP, the higher the damage.

Curse.desc: Ghosts lose 50% of max HP and curse the opponent; Non-Ghosts raise Attack, Defense and lower Speed.

Magma Storm.desc: Traps opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

Electro Ball.desc: The faster the user, the stronger the attack.

Volt Tackle.desc: User receives recoil damage. May paralyze opponent.

Assurance.desc: Power doubles if opponent already took damage in the same turn.

G-Max One Blow.desc: Urshifu Single-Strike Style-exclusive G-Max Move. Strikes through Max Guard and Protect.

Max Wyrmwind.desc: Dragon type Dynamax move. Lowers the target's Attack.

Quiver Dance.desc: Raises user's Special Attack, Special Defense and Speed.

Pollen Puff.desc: Deals damage to opponent or restores HP of teammate.

Dire Claw.desc: May poison, paralyze or put the opponent to sleep.

Fell Stinger.desc: Drastically raises user's Attack if target is KO'd.

Eternabeam.desc: User can't move on the next turn.

Uproar.desc: User attacks for 3 turns and prevents sleep.

Fusion Bolt.desc: Power increases if Fusion Flare is used in the same turn.

Power Swap.desc: User and opponent swap Attack and Special Attack.

Dark Void.desc: Puts all adjacent opponents to sleep.

Retaliate.desc: Inflicts double damage if a teammate fainted on the last turn.

G-Max Foam Burst.desc: Kingler-exclusive G-Max Move. Harshly lowers opponents' Speed.

Bug Bite.desc: Receives the effect from the opponent's held berry.

Wonder Room.desc: Swaps every Pokémon's Defense and Special Defense for 5 turns.

Power Split.desc: Averages Attack and Special Attack with the target.

G-Max Volcalith.desc: Coalossal-exclusive G-Max Move. Deals damage for 4 turns.

Max Strike.desc: Normal type Dynamax move. Lowers the target's Speed.

Tar Shot.desc: Lowers the opponent's Speed and makes them weaker to Fire-type moves.

First Impression.desc: Although this move has great power, it only works the first turn the user is in battle.

Poltergeist.desc: Fails if the target doesn’t have an item.

Revenge.desc: Power increases if user was hit first.

Guardian of Alola.desc: Tapu-exclusive Z-move. Cuts opponent's HP by 75%.

Extreme Evoboost.desc: Eevee-exclusive Z-Move. Sharply raises all stats.

Heavy Slam.desc: The heavier the user, the stronger the attack.

Sappy Seed.desc: Drains HP from opponent each turn.

Low Kick.desc: The heavier the opponent, the stronger the attack.

Throat Chop.desc: Prevents use of sound moves for two turns.

Parting Shot.desc: Lowers opponent's Attack and Special Attack then switches out.

Recover.desc: User recovers half its max HP.

Super Fang.desc: Always takes off half of the opponent's HP.

Judgment.desc: Type depends on the Arceus Plate being held.

Max Rockfall.desc: Rock type Dynamax move. Summons a sandstorm.

Spectral Thief.desc: The user hides in the target's shadow, steals the target's stat boosts, and then attacks.

Bind.desc: Traps opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

Constrict.desc: May lower opponent's Speed by one stage.

Shell Side Arm.desc: May poison opponent. Inflicts either Special or Physical damage, whichever is better.

Ice Fang.desc: May cause flinching and/or freeze opponent.

Pain Split.desc: The user's and opponent's HP becomes the average of both.

Burning Jealousy.desc: Hits all opponents, and burns any that have had their stats boosted.

Shore Up.desc: The user regains up to half of its max HP. It restores more HP in a sandstorm.

Work Up.desc: Raises user's Attack and Special Attack.

Psychic Fangs.desc: The user bites the target with its psychic capabilities. This can also destroy Light Screen and Reflect.

Lock-On.desc: User's next attack is guaranteed to hit.

Water Pledge.desc: Added effects appear if preceded by Fire Pledge or succeeded by Grass Pledge.

Torment.desc: Opponent cannot use the same move in a row.

G-Max Drum Solo.desc: Rillaboom-exclusive G-Max Move. Ignores target's ability.

Glacial Lance.desc: The user attacks by hurling a blizzard-cloaked icicle lance at opposing Pokémon.

Whirlpool.desc: Traps opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

Electrify.desc: Changes the target's move to Electric type.
